<CELL>slaves of all ages.</CELL>
</ROW>
</TABLE></P>
<P>543,438 inhabitants, exclusive of the 8 coun|ties from which were no returns. In these 8 coun|ties in the years 1779 and 1780, were 3,161 mi|litia. Say then,
<TABLE>
