<DIV1 N="9" TYPE="query">
<PB N="130" REF="027162_0134_0FD528F8AB44DBC8">
<HEAD>QUERY IX.</HEAD>
<P>THE number and condition of the militia and regular troops, and their pay?</P>
<P>The following is a state of the militia, taken from returns of 1780 and 1781, except in those counties marked with an asterisk, the returns from which are somewhat older.</P>
